<subsection xml:id="subsec-geometric-product">
<title>Geometric Product</title>
<paragraphs xml:id="para-geom-definition">
<title>Definition</title>
<p>A <term>geometric product</term> between <m>\mathbf{a},\mathbf{b}\in \mathcal{V}_n</m> where <m>\mathcal{V_n} \sube \mathbb{R}^n </m> is given by:</p>
<me>\mathbf{a}\mathbf{b} = \mathbf{a}\cdot\mathbf{b} + \mathbf{a}\wedge\mathbf{b}</me>
<note>
<p>The geometric product can be decomposed into symmetric (dot product) and antisymmetric (wedge product) parts.</p>
</note>
</paragraphs>
